author: dlr
msg: Per discussion on dev list, revert r18040, re-instating GCC 4.0.1's
compilation warnings (which turn into build failures when using -Wall
-Werror).  The Plan is to add compilation flags (likely
-Wno-uninitialized) for GCC which disable this type of warning.
